@page "/chat-pdf"

<PageTitle>Chat with PDF Online — Ask Your Document Anything | PdfToolStack</PageTitle>
<HeadContent>
    <meta name="description" content="Chat with any PDF document using AI. Ask questions, get summaries, find specific information instantly. Powered by Claude AI. Free to try." />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://pdftoolstack.com/chat-with-pdf" />
</HeadContent>

<div class="lp-page">
    <section class="lp-hero lp-chat-hero">
        <div class="lp-hero-inner">
            <div class="lp-badge lp-badge-purple">AI-Powered</div>
            <h1 class="lp-h1">Stop reading<br /><span class="lp-accent-purple">the whole document.</span></h1>
            <p class="lp-sub">Upload a PDF and ask it anything. "What's the payment term?" "When does this contract expire?" "Summarize section 4." Get instant, accurate answers without reading 80 pages.</p>
            <div class="lp-cta-row">
                <a href="/chat-with-pdf" class="lp-btn-primary lp-btn-purple">
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z" /></svg>
                    Chat with My PDF Free
                </a>
                <span class="lp-trust-inline">✓ 5 free chats/month · No signup · Private</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Animated chat visual -->
        <div class="lp-chat-visual">
            <div class="lp-chat-container">
                <div class="lp-chat-doc-bar">
                    <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#7C3AED" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z" /><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8" /></svg>
                    contract_2024.pdf · 48 pages
                </div>
                <div class="lp-chat-messages">
                    <div class="lp-chat-msg lp-chat-user" style="animation-delay:0.3s;">What's the payment term?</div>
                    <div class="lp-chat-msg lp-chat-ai" style="animation-delay:0.9s;">Payment is due <strong>net 30 days</strong> from invoice date. Late payments incur 1.5% monthly interest per Section 4.2.</div>
                    <div class="lp-chat-msg lp-chat-user" style="animation-delay:1.8s;">When does it expire?</div>
                    <div class="lp-chat-msg lp-chat-ai" style="animation-delay:2.4s;">This agreement expires on <strong>December 31, 2025</strong> and auto-renews for 12-month periods unless either party gives 60 days written notice.</div>
                    <div class="lp-chat-typing" style="animation-delay:3.0s;">
                        <div class="lp-typing-dot"></div>
                        <div class="lp-typing-dot"></div>
                        <div class="lp-typing-dot"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="lp-section lp-pain-section">
        <div class="lp-section-inner">
            <h2 class="lp-h2">The document search nightmare</h2>
            <div class="lp-cards-3">
                <div class="lp-card"><div class="lp-card-icon">📖</div><h3>80-page contracts</h3><p>Legal, financial, and technical documents are long. Finding one specific clause means reading everything — or missing it entirely.</p></div>
                <div class="lp-card"><div class="lp-card-icon">🔍</div><h3>Ctrl+F only finds exact words</h3><p>Search for "termination" but the clause says "cessation of services." You miss it. Chat finds it by meaning.</p></div>
                <div class="lp-card"><div class="lp-card-icon">⏱️</div><h3>Summaries take 30 minutes</h3><p>Reading, highlighting, summarizing a dense report manually. AI does it in 15 seconds.</p></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="lp-final-cta-section">
        <div class="lp-final-inner">
            <h2>Ask your document instead of reading it.</h2>
            <p>Get instant answers from any PDF — free, powered by Claude AI.</p>
            <a href="/chat-with-pdf" class="lp-btn-primary lp-btn-purple lp-btn-lg">Chat with PDF Free</a>
            <p class="lp-fine">5 free chats/month · No signup · Files deleted in 1 hour</p>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
